high_descs: turn to the left go right towards the white table
pick up the knife from the white table
turn around to the right go forward towards the sink
slice the tomato that is inside the sink
put the knife inside the sink
pick up a slice of tomato that is in the sink
turn to the right towards the microwave
open the microwave door put the slice of tomato heat it up get the slice back out

put the slice of tomato on top of the white table

high_descs: Go to the table to the left of the red waste basket.
Pick up the knife from the table that is between the other two knives.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Slice the tomato that is in the sink.
Place the knife into the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice from the sink.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave, run it, and then remove the tomato.
Turn right and go to the white table that is on the left.
Put the tomato on the table in between the bowls.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, microwave it, and bring it to a table.
